# Development Guide

## Setup
1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies
3. Copy .env.example to .env
4. Start development server

## Workflow
1. Create feature branch from dev/main
2. Make changes
3. Test locally
4. Create PR to dev/main
5. After review, merge
6. Deploy to QA
7. Deploy to production

## Commands
- `npm run dev` - Start development server
- `npm test` - Run tests
- `npm run lint` - Lint code
- `./scripts/new-feature.sh <name>` - Create new feature branch
- `./scripts/deploy-qa.sh` - Deploy to QA
- `./scripts/deploy-prod.sh` - Deploy to production
